name: Epiphonus

name: Oriscus
column12: Where should this bbox division into vertical bboxes be done? Heuristic pitch finding (how is that working? because it is getting the pitch of the individual neume-components correcly even having only one bbox for the whole neume) or MEI Encoding job?

name: Quilisma
column12: This file is received by the MEI Encoding job, so it can do the mapping of the IC class into both the MEI code (for encoding the <neume>) and the width column (for dividing the bbox and encoding the <zone>s)
